title: BRIEF-Proteostasis Receives Endorsement From Cystic Fibrosis Foundation For Study Of PTI-428 In CF Subjects On Background Symdeko Therapy
text:
Market News April 17, 2018 / 12:08 PM / Updated 10 minutes ago BRIEF-Proteostasis Receives Endorsement From Cystic Fibrosis Foundation For Study Of PTI-428 In CF Subjects On Background Symdeko Therapy Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 17 (Reuters) - Proteostasis Therapeutics Inc: 
* PROTEOSTASIS RECEIVES ENDORSEMENT FROM THE CYSTIC FIBROSIS FOUNDATION’S THERAPEUTIC DEVELOPMENT NETWORK FOR THE STUDY OF THE COMPANY’S AMPLIFIER, PTI-428, IN CF SUBJECTS ON BACKGROUND SYMDEKO™ THERAPY Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
